8781 Value |= op;
8782 // op: enc
8783 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8784 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(280375465082880));
8785 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(255));
8786 break;
8787 }
8788 case SystemZ::InsnVRI: {
8789 // op: V1
8790 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
8791 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 36;
8792 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 7;
8793 // op: V2
8794 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
8795 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 32;
8796 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 6;
8797 // op: I3
8798 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(3), Fixups, STI);
8799 op &= UINT64_C(4095);
8800 op <<= 20;
8801 Value |= op;
8802 // op: M4
8803 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(4), Fixups, STI);
8804 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8805 op <<= 12;
8806 Value |= op;
8807 // op: M5
8808 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(5), Fixups, STI);
8809 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8810 op <<= 16;
8811 Value |= op;
8812 // op: enc
8813 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8814 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(280375465082880));
8815 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(255));
8816 break;
8817 }
8818 case SystemZ::InsnVRR: {
8819 // op: V1
8820 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
8821 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 36;
8822 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 7;
8823 // op: V2
8824 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(2), Fixups, STI);
8825 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 32;
8826 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 6;
8827 // op: V3
8828 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(3), Fixups, STI);
8829 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 28;
8830 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 5;
8831 // op: M4
8832 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(4), Fixups, STI);
8833 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8834 op <<= 12;
8835 Value |= op;
8836 // op: M5
8837 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(5), Fixups, STI);
8838 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8839 op <<= 16;
8840 Value |= op;
8841 // op: M6
8842 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(6), Fixups, STI);
8843 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8844 op <<= 20;
8845 Value |= op;
8846 // op: enc
8847 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8848 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(280375465082880));
8849 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(255));
8850 break;
8851 }
8852 case SystemZ::InsnVRV: {
8853 // op: V1
8854 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
8855 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 36;
8856 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 7;
8857 // op: VBD2
8858 op = getBDVAddr12Encoding(MI, 2, Fixups, STI);
8859 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(1048575)) << 16;
8860 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(1048576)) >> 10;
8861 // op: M3
8862 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(5), Fixups, STI);
8863 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8864 op <<= 12;
8865 Value |= op;
8866 // op: enc
8867 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8868 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(280375465082880));
8869 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(255));
8870 break;
8871 }
8872 case SystemZ::InsnVRX: {
8873 // op: V1
8874 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(1), Fixups, STI);
8875 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(15)) << 36;
8876 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(16)) << 7;
8877 // op: XBD2
8878 op = getBDXAddr12Encoding(MI, 2, Fixups, STI);
8879 op &= UINT64_C(1048575);
8880 op <<= 16;
8881 Value |= op;
8882 // op: M3
8883 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(5), Fixups, STI);
8884 op &= UINT64_C(15);
8885 op <<= 12;
8886 Value |= op;
8887 // op: enc
8888 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8889 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(280375465082880));
8890 Value |= (op & UINT64_C(255));
8891 break;
8892 }
8893 case SystemZ::B:
8894 case SystemZ::BAsmE:
8895 case SystemZ::BAsmH:
8896 case SystemZ::BAsmHE:
8897 case SystemZ::BAsmL:
8898 case SystemZ::BAsmLE:
8899 case SystemZ::BAsmLH:
8900 case SystemZ::BAsmM:
8901 case SystemZ::BAsmNE:
8902 case SystemZ::BAsmNH:
8903 case SystemZ::BAsmNHE:
8904 case SystemZ::BAsmNL:
8905 case SystemZ::BAsmNLE:
8906 case SystemZ::BAsmNLH:
8907 case SystemZ::BAsmNM:
8908 case SystemZ::BAsmNO:
8909 case SystemZ::BAsmNP:
8910 case SystemZ::BAsmNZ:
8911 case SystemZ::BAsmO:
8912 case SystemZ::BAsmP:
8913 case SystemZ::BAsmZ: {
8914 // op: XBD2
8915 op = getBDXAddr12Encoding(MI, 0, Fixups, STI);
8916 op &= UINT64_C(1048575);
8917 Value |= op;
8918 break;
8919 }
8920 case SystemZ::BI:
8921 case SystemZ::BIAsmE:
8922 case SystemZ::BIAsmH:
8923 case SystemZ::BIAsmHE:
8924 case SystemZ::BIAsmL:
8925 case SystemZ::BIAsmLE:
8926 case SystemZ::BIAsmLH:
8927 case SystemZ::BIAsmM:
8928 case SystemZ::BIAsmNE:
8929 case SystemZ::BIAsmNH:
8930 case SystemZ::BIAsmNHE:
8931 case SystemZ::BIAsmNL:
8932 case SystemZ::BIAsmNLE:
8933 case SystemZ::BIAsmNLH:
8934 case SystemZ::BIAsmNM:
8935 case SystemZ::BIAsmNO:
8936 case SystemZ::BIAsmNP:
8937 case SystemZ::BIAsmNZ:
8938 case SystemZ::BIAsmO:
8939 case SystemZ::BIAsmP:
8940 case SystemZ::BIAsmZ: {
8941 // op: XBD2
8942 op = getBDXAddr20Encoding(MI, 0, Fixups, STI);
8943 op &= UINT64_C(268435455);
8944 op <<= 8;
8945 Value |= op;
8946 break;
8947 }
8948 case SystemZ::InsnE: {
8949 // op: enc
8950 op = getMachineOpValue(MI, MI.getOperand(0), Fixups, STI);
8951 op &= UINT64_C(65535);
8952 Value |= op;
8953 break;
8954 }
8955 default:
8956 std::string msg;
8957 raw_string_ostream Msg(msg);
8958 Msg << "Not supported instr: " << MI;
8959 report_fatal_error(Msg.str());
8960 }
8961 return Value;
8962}

12296
12297 assert(Inst.getOpcode() < 3082);
12298 const FeatureBitset &RequiredFeatures = FeatureBitsets[RequiredFeaturesRefs[Inst.getOpcode()]];
12299 FeatureBitset MissingFeatures =
12300 (AvailableFeatures & RequiredFeatures) ^
12301 RequiredFeatures;
12302 if (MissingFeatures.any()) {
12303 std::ostringstream Msg;
12304 Msg << "Attempting to emit " << MCII.getName(Inst.getOpcode()).str()
12305 << " instruction but the ";
12306 for (unsigned i = 0, e = MissingFeatures.size(); i != e; ++i)
12307 if (MissingFeatures.test(i))
12308 Msg << SubtargetFeatureNames[i] << " ";
12309 Msg << "predicate(s) are not met";
12310 report_fatal_error(Msg.str());
12311 }

12314 (void)MCII;
12315#endif // NDEBUG
12316}
